Governors in Nyanza will hold the first rally to drum up support for the building bridges initiative in Kisii county on the 10th of January. James Ongwae the convening committee chairman says the leaders will gather to listen to emerging issues from the report and pick up new suggestions. Homa bay governor Cyprian Awiti and hisÂ 
Nyamira counterpart john Nyagarama said the state must integrate public participation to its entire governance strategy if it wants to engage the people in order to monitor its implementation.